00:00:54.890 --> 00:01:02.020
While this is heating, I'm going to add the
juice of one lime to this.

00:01:02.020 --> 00:01:03.950
There's the other half of my lime.

00:01:03.950 --> 00:01:09.780
I just used a regular plain old pot.

00:01:09.780 --> 00:01:14.360
