a special type of nonstick.

00:01:16.610 --> 00:01:20.150
It's called a green pot, but you can use any
pot.

00:01:20.150 --> 00:01:24.729
Now that all my rice is coated with oil and
has a nice sheen on it,

00:01:24.729 --> 00:01:35.569
I'm going to go ahead and add my water, so
now I'm going to put the lid on

00:01:35.569 --> 00:01:37.200
