done and we're going to finish it

00:01:41.369 --> 00:01:46.450
up with cilantro, a little bit of salt, and
a touch of lime, so rice is now

00:01:46.450 --> 00:01:47.450
done.

00:01:47.450 --> 00:01:48.929
I just put it in this pot right here.

00:01:48.929 --> 00:01:53.890
